      Mahm£dah:  Kultu, 'khshi an takhirrini.'"

"The effects of patience" (or aloes) quoth one "are
praiseworthy!" Quoth I, "Much I fear lest it make me stool."
Mahm£dah is not only un laxatif, but a slang name for a
confection of aloes.

