Ahmad, 'Amm£r for 'Amr£. So the fem. form, Fa''£lah, e.g.
Khadd£gah = little Khadijah and Naff£sah=little Nafisah; Ar'£rah
= little clitoris - whereas in Heb. it is an incrementative e.g.
